&lt;li&gt;Port size: 1/8&quot; to 1/2&quot;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Body Ported&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Available as air operated, internal and external pilot solenoid&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Operating pressure range: -14 to 145 psi&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

